Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,== Dialogue ============================

Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing quite like ice hockey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But nearly everyone there is a stranger.\NI'm not sure I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You won't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be bored all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The other girls will be there.\NThey said they'd be back next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao, do you have plans next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just gonna read manga.\NAnd that's fine, but outdoors is outdoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, the hockey rink\Nis inside. If anything, it's indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have such an\Nold photo on your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad scanned it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so cute, Nao. My dad always\Nsaid you had a knack for ice hockey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,While I appreciate you carrying\Nthat photo everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart was set on figure\Nskating, so I switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I was no good at spin\Njumps, I quit skating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not the point\NI'm trying to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like jumping\Nis useful in ice hockey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you pushing me to play so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, although I can't deny that playing\Nhockey again felt nostalgic and fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mostly just wanna do\Nsomething with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Here it comes, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So? I'm begging you!\NC'mon, I don't wanna go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! How does a Monkey Complete sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't think the Monkey\Nwill work next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! I hooked her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an ice hockey book?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get your hands moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was talking to Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've made good progress,\Nso you're allowed a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to brush up\Nbefore the next trial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it in the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you snatched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! Next class, I think\Nwe'll be training for speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, those stretches we did\Nfelt awfully like dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually... It might\Ncome in handy for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Break's over! If we don't finish these,\Nwe can't show 'em off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our president's the furthest behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell who's president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! The TV show I was talking\Nabout is coming this weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. We're glad that you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a program about the {\i1}ryokan {\i0}and\NKinugawa's charms and specialties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They took Grandma's suggestion and\Nare doing a bit about our family farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Mami's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My dad's just a salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But your papa is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's in those bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, Ayaka. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the senior\Nhostess of Shikiootoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the future hostess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, the beautiful, next-gen sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And... their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And in those outfits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get "Team Next-Gen" and their\Nfriends to show us around the {\i1}ryokan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These are from my family's Yanagida Farms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We pride ourselves on our sweet\Nand juicy strawberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat just one and you'll\Nsee what she means!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit of condensed milk\Nmakes them all the more sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's best to eat 'em plain,\Nstraight from nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping! You guys made it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we're filming again tomorrow.\NThink you could help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? Oh, dear me!\NI've got important plans tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like a famous actress, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Important plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we're going to\Nan ice hockey trial class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey trial class?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you serious?!\NYes, of course! With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about happy.\NWhat was that call about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, a TV show from Tokyo is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanna cover our trial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And? You agreed to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm great at PR!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What to wear tomorrow?!\NMaybe I should get my hair done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know they're not coming\Nto cover you, but the class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Riko. You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao! Knock-knock.\NComing in! Okay! {\i1}Kachak{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "What now?" me. You promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now! Let's get you ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! I can change on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks nothing like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you guys,\Nwe'll be on TV! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Tokyo variety program!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, go change into your jerseys.\NYou know where, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Brr! It's like Alaska in here!\NNot that I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm shocked you've got\Nsuch a beautiful stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikko Dream Monkeys\Nis a pro ice hockey team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They were founded in 1925.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been supported by both fans\Nand businesses over its many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that old, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our team color represents our love\Nof the community and their love for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the team has many\Nplayers who grew up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This class is us giving back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought it would be a good\Nway to engage with the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope that they'll enjoy ice hockey,\Nbecome interested, and join the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And while that's our goal,\Neven if they don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we hope that they experience\Nthe thrill of hockey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko's actually serious today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I read that profile of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When did she give them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You played hockey yourself, Matsunaga?\NAnd represented Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you saw that part?!\NBelieve it or not, I was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh. She's back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born here in Nikko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I played hockey when I was little,\Nand have loved it ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm single and available!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with stretches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--They're all having fun.\N--Three, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Seems so.\N--Three, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm totally killing it!\N--Three, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--What an evil face, Yoko.\N--Four, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yup! I can feel my arms stretching out!\N--Four, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is side-walk. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--Two, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,--This is totally a dance.\N--Two, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--It sure is.\N--Three, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ice hockey stretches sure are odd.\N--Three, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah, well...\N--Four, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--Four, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--Five, two, three, four, five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Quit with that face.\N--Five, two, three, four, five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Edge control. It's important to\Nmaster balance when skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, you're good at skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is passing practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginuma! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful today.\NOof! Whoa! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko Saginuma, was it? Where have I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, any plans for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to increase the\Npopularity of ice hockey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very much a minor sport in Japan,\Nbut ice hockey is truly fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone out there\Nto see for themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. After coming here today,\Nit does seem pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then you should\Ndefinitely go see a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the teamwork, the speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The puck movement on the rink\Nis something you just have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the girls get fierce and competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The way they fight and steal\Nthe puck--it's an intense sport!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee if you watch just once,\Nyou'll see how interesting it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, we'll pack this entire arena\Nwith fans. That's the dream I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope your dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, gather up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be challenging you\Nin a new way today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to get comfortable with one\Nof hockey's best highlights--its speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Skate as fast as you can towards\Nthe goal, touch the line, and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! We went so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Faster than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi skates so gracefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko Saginuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is your father one of our\Nold players, Kenji Saginuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me that sooner! Is he doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! He's coaching at a college in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear! So, what do you think?!\NWill you guys come back next week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is "okey-dokey" not gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,--Saginuma!\N--Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so cool how you slid\Nright in and caught Ayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And how you stopped\NSis' terrible passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry about my wreck of a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me a wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your little sister's mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the big sis now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginuma, you've played hockey before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ever since I was little... with Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our coach seemed to know your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! He played for the Dream Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a thoroughbred!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But after Nao switched to figure skating,\Nit was boring by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Figure skating?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're so elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You skate so gracefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Like nobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it! She's like\Na swan on the ice! Glide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you're all from Kinugawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! My house is a {\i1}ryokan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All these cute girls\Ncoming to the trial class...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginuma's daughter being one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That TV show coming to film...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the goddess of luck\Nbe smiling upon me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that good things are happening,\Nbut don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The good life rarely lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can overcome whatever\Nmisfortunes come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, unhappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I somewhat envy your positive attitude,\Nbut it does get annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, all. You were a great help today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know when the program airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! We can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Ice hockey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys look pretty\Ngood at it. Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,--See you!\N--Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yup!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more than last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginuma and Takagi seem like nice people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi's a bit shy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For ice hockey, you need\Nsix people to play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there're six of us who come,\Ncouldn't we form a team?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We could!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe we can join Dream Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk to 'em next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet those two will be up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami? Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Manaka. Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm just reviewing\Nwhat we did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels weird! If only studying\Nfor school was this easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't join the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, because after the second\Nsemester, I'm transferring schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do this anymore?\NWhat's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly how it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste the best there is,\Nright here in Japan!
